@startuml Candidate_Skills

title Candidate - Skills (Module E, C)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng Viên"

rectangle "SKILLS" {
    usecase "View System\nSkills" as C12
    usecase "Add Skill\nto CV" as E4
    usecase "View My\nCV Skills" as E5
    usecase "Update Skill\nProficiency" as E6
    usecase "Remove Skill\nfrom CV" as E7
}

Candidate --> C12: 1. View system skills
Candidate --> E4: 2. Add skill
Candidate --> E5: 3. View CV skills
E5 --> E6: 4. Update proficiency
E5 --> E7: 5. Remove skill

note right of E4
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
